sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_012_CSMS (Section 3.4.4, Table 132, Page 117-118/176)
    Note over CP,CS: Remote Stop Charging Session
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Reusable State: Charging (Table 201, requires Authorized)

    CS->>CP: 1. RemoteStopTransaction.req (transactionId)
    CP-->>CS: 2. RemoteStopTransaction.conf (status=Accepted)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Accepted

    CP->>CS: 3. StopTransaction.req (transactionId, meterStop, timestamp, reason=Remote)
    CS-->>CP: 4. StopTransaction.conf
    Note over CP: Validation: reason must be Remote

    CP->>CS: 5. StatusNotification.req (status=Finishing, errorCode=NoError)
    CS-->>CP: 6. StatusNotification.conf
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Finishing

    Note over CP: [EV driver unplugs the cable]

    CP->>CS: 7. StatusNotification.req (status=Available, errorCode=NoError)
    CS-->>CP: 8. StatusNotification.conf
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Available
